txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Albino skin from the boars surrounding Echad Mirobel. Deliver the items to Maegamiel at Echad Mirobel in the southern section of Eregion.
'We will make good use of these. Thank you.'
'Furs and skins have many uses. Would you collect some for us?'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Albino Skin
Maegamiel at Echad Mirobel has requested that albino skin be delivered to her at the Elf-ruins in the southern reaches of Eregion.
Deliver the albino skin to Maegamiel at Echad Mirobel in southern Eregion
You have accepted a task to deliver albino skin from the boars surrounding Echad Mirobel to Maegamiel. Maegamiel defends Echad Mirobel in the southern area of Eregion.
Wanted: Albino skin from the boars surrounding Echad Mirobel.
